These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, game, davidoff, bongani, vegafina, chaman
6 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, goldfish, pony, bird, fish
 1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
 2. the bongani-smoker is not the owner of the mouse##6
 3. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
 6. the owner of the pony is not the game-smoker##6
 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 9. the owner of the fish is not the vegafina-smoker##6
10. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the vegafina-smoker##5
11. the owner of the fish is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
12. the davidoff-smoker is between the owner of the bird and the montecristo-smoker##2
13. the game-smoker is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
14. the owner of the rat is not the bongani-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |      5      |      6      |
| Hobby         | bongani | chaman | game     | davidoff | montecristo | vegafina |
| Nationality   | pony    | mouse   | bird | fish | goldfish    | rat   |

