.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: jazz, d&b, techno, hip-hop, gospel, reggae
The people use 6 different means of transport: tram, scooter, skateboard, jet-ski, van, bus
 1. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 2. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
 4. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the fan jazz##5
 5. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
 6. the fan d&b is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 7. the fan reggae is on the right of the fan d&b##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 9. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the fan d&b##1
10. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
11. the fan gospel is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
13. the person driving the skateboard is the fan hip-hop##1
14. the fan techno is not the person driving the skateboard##6
15. the fan jazz is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the bus##2
16. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |    3    |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Food    | techno | jazz     | gospel   | hip-hop | d&b      | reggae  |
| Hobby   | bus   | van | tram | skateboard  | scooter | jet-ski |

