.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-3::.
6 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, goldfish, horse, ferret, dog
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: punk, disco, pop, r&b, reggae, folk
 1. the owner of the dog is the fan pop##1
 2. the owner of the horse is not the fan folk##6
 3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the fan disco##5
 4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the fan r&b##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is the fan reggae##1
 6. the fan r&b is between the fan folk and the owner of the ferret##2
 7. the fan pop is on the left or right of the fan punk##3
 8. the fan disco is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
 9. the fan punk is the owner of the mouse##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality   | ferret  | horse | frog    | goldfish | mouse | dog |
| Sport         | disco | r&b | folk | reggae     | punk  | pop    |

