.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-4::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: red, ebony, yellow, orange, blue, brown
6 different games are played: scrabble, whist, billiard, go, snooker, mah-jongg
 1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 7. the person who likes red is not the person playing billiard##6
 8. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who likes red##6
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
11. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
12. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
13. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who likes red##5
14. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |   2    |       3        |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food   | blue | orange | brown         | yellow | red     | ebony      |
| Job    | go   | mah-jongg | snooker | scrabble    | whist | billiard |

