 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsorchid is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 5. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 6. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
10. the person drinking juice is not the person who growsorchid##6
11. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
