.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-6::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, april, december, september, may, january
City: new-york, marseilles, venice, prague, london, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person traveling to london is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 4. the person traveling to venice is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person traveling to london##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
12. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
13. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |  3   |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Beverage   | december  | may | september | january | february | april |
| Pet        | prague | hamburg  | venice | marseilles | london  | new-york          |

