 3. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the russian##3
 4. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the tower house##3
 6. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
 7. the tower house is on the left of the italian##1
 8. the american is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the russian is not the farmhouse house##6
10. the cottage house is on the far left##1
11. the french is the farmhouse house##1
