6 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, blend, chaman, oliveros, pall-mall, bongani
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, collecting, card-games, singing, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an odd position##4
 6. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
10. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the oliveros-smoker##1
13. the person who's hobby is singing is not the pall-mall-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |   4    |    5    |      6      |
| Beverage      | oliveros | chaman | blend | bongani | pall-mall | vegafina |
| Music-Genre   | card-games  | filmmaking   | collecting | singing  | drawing  | chess        |

