.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-19::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, skydiving, cooking, writing, card-games
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, boat, quad-bike, van, scooter, taxi
 1. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 7. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 8. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
14. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
15. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
16. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person driving the boat##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | skydiving     | puzzles | card-games  | cooking | writing   | collecting |
| Sport         | airplane | taxi  | quad-bike | van | scooter | boat  |

