.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-6-20::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, marigold, bellflower, amaryllis, daffodil
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, montecristo, ritmeester, game, baccarat, bolivar
 1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is not the baccarat-smoker##6
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
 7. the game-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who growsmarigold##5
 9. the bolivar-smoker is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
10. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who growsdaffodil##1
11. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
12. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
13. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
14. the swisher-smoker is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | amaryllis | daffodil | marigold | daisy | balloon-flower | bellflower |
| Music-Genre   | swisher | ritmeester        | baccarat     | bolivar | game      | montecristo |

 